# TC16: LowBatteryDetected2
# Precondition: BoostMode, cleaning in progress
# Action: detect battery level below threshold
# Expected: enter LowBatteryMode, cleaner and motor deactivate, CleanerDriver mode off
# Note: BoostMode entry requires Controller::dustDetected() or equivalent boost PR implementation.
power
start
dust
expect power on
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
expect motor moving
battery 5
low-battery
expect power on
expect mode LowBatteryMode
expect battery 5
expect motor stopped
expect motorForward false
expect cleaner off
expect cleanerMode off
exit
